Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity

Class InferenceRequestImage

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.InferenceRequestImage
public class InferenceRequestImage extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents image data for an inference request.
This class encapsulates various image data formats and properties used in making inference requests.
It supports multiple input types such as URL, base64 encoded strings, or numpy arrays.

  • Field Details

    • type

      private String type
      The type of image data provided.
      • "url" - the image is provided as a URL.
      • "base64" - the image is provided as a base64 encoded string.
      • "numpy" - the image is provided as a numpy array.

    • value

      private String value
      The image value.
      For URLs, this will be the URL of the image. For base64, this will be the base64 encoded string. For numpy arrays, it could represent a serialized array.

    • path

      private String path
      The file path of the image.
      This could be used when referencing the image location from the file system.

    • prefix

      private String prefix
      Prefix to be used with the image URL or file path.
      This could be useful for appending a prefix to the image path or URL when required.

    • newDimensions

      private InferenceImageDimensions newDimensions
      The new dimensions of the image after potential resizing.
      This represents the width and height after resizing, if applicable.

    • originalDimensions

      private InferenceImageDimensions originalDimensions
      The original dimensions of the image.
      This represents the original width and height of the image before any transformations.

    • resized

      private Boolean resized
      Indicates whether the image has been resized.
      This is a boolean flag that shows if the image's dimensions have been altered from the original.
